(27, 12, 7, 4, '2018-10-16 17:16:12', 'Betameson N', '', 'Betameson-N-1.jpg', '', '', 22, 0, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">COMPOSITION</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Betameson-N&reg; cream : Each gram cream contains Betamethasone<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Dipropionate USP equivalent to 1mg Betamethasone base and<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Neomycin Sulphate BP 5mg.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">PHARMACOLOGY</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Betamethasone is an active topical corticosteroid which produces a rapid response in those inammatory dermatoses that are normally responsive to topical corticosteroid therapy, and is often effective in the less responsive conditions such as psoriasis. Neomycin sulphate is a broad spectrum bactericidal antibiotic eective against the majority of bacteria commonly associated with skin infections.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">INDICATION</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Eczema, prurigo nodularis, psoriasis, neurodermatoses, seborrhoeic dermatitis, contact sensitivity reactions, systemic steroid therapy in generalized erythroderma, secondarily infected insect bites &amp; anal &amp; genital intertrigo; specially when scondary bacterial infection is present.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Apply sparingly 2-3 times daily, reducing frequency as condition responds</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">SIDE EFFECT</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Local atrophic changes in the skin such as thinning, striae, &amp; dilatation of the supercial blood vessels, sucient systemic absorption to produce the features of hypercorticism &amp; suppression of the HPA axis.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">STORAGE CONDITION</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Protect from light and moisture. Keep out of reach of children.</p>', '<table class=\"shop_attributes\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; width: 645px; margin-bottom: 1em; border-color: #ececec; border-spacing: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 0px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec; line-height: 1.05; font-size: 0.9em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;\">PRODUCTS TYPE</th>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.5em 0px 0.5em 0.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec; line-height: 1.3; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666666;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.5em 0px;\">Cream</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<th style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.5em 0.5em 0.5em 0px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec; line-height: 1.05; font-size: 0.9em; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;\">GENERIC NAMES</th>\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0.5em 0px 0.5em 0.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid #ececec; line-height: 1.3; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666666;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.5em 0px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; tou